Package: RobustBetaTests
Type: Package
Title: Robust Hypothesis Testing for Beta Regression Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gabriel Araujo
Maintainer: Gabriel Araujo <gabriel@example.com>
Description: Computational routines for robust hypothesis testing in beta regression models.
    This package provides functions for fitting beta regression models with robust
    methods and performing robust hypothesis tests including Wald, Score, and 
    Likelihood Ratio tests with robust variance estimation.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: stats, MASS
RoxygenNote: 7.0.0